                        "description": "The separation was performed using the ACQUITY UPLC BEH C18 column (1.7 \u03bcm, 2.1 \u00d7 100 mm). The elution solvents were water+0.01% formic acid (A) and acetonitrile/methanol (19:1)+0.01% formic acid (B). The elution gradient over 20 min at a flow rate of 450 \u00b5l/min was as follows: 0-2 min (20% B), 2-3 min (20-25% B), 3-6 min (25% B), 6-8 min (25-35% B), 8-11.5 min (35% B), 11.5-18 min (35-99% B), 18-19 min (99% B), and 19-20 min (99-20% B).",
